    "description": "<p>Huabao Flavours &amp; Fragrances Co., Ltd. was founded in 1996 and has been successfully listed on the Shenzhen Stock Exchange. Huabao is principally engaged in the research &amp; development, production, sales and services of tobacco flavours, food flavours, daily chemical flavours and food ingredients; with a total of 39 subordinate companies globally. From 2014 - 2020, Huabao is ranked as No. 1 in Flavour &amp; Fragrance industry in China.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Wih the vision of \"Flavour Your Life\", the company insists on the enterprise spirits of \"Innovation, Pragmatism, Loyalty and Cooperation\", and the integrates domestic and foreign scientific research resources with international vision, to provide products style system solution and comprehensive technical services for customers.&nbsp;</p>",
